@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_txwsnv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v1 + 0.38 - v1 + 0.78)))
    v0 = (tmp + ((v2 + 0.22 / v0 + 0.91) - (v0 + 0.43 - v0 + 0.40)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
